  line: string - a string with serialized key-value pairs as &ldquo;key1=value1;key2=value2;&hellip;&rdquo;
Example: &ldquo;Key1=123;Key2=ABC;Key3=2016-09-16T00:00:00.00Z&rdquo; returns: ConfigParams - a new ConfigParams object.  FromTuples Creates a new ConfigParams object filled with provided key-value pairs called tuples. Tuples parameters contain a sequence of key1, value1, key2, value2, &hellip; pairs.
See StringValueMap.fromTuplesArray
